    <p>Q-1: Strings are made up of smaller pieces (the characters). This makes strings an example of a _____ type. <var/>  </p></statement><setup><var><condition string="^\s*compound\s*$"><feedback><p>Correct!</p></feedback></condition><condition string="^\s*.*\s*$"><feedback><p>Try again!</p></feedback></condition></var></setup></exercise>
